208  nh_.subscribe("recognized_object_array", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::listenDetectedObjects, this);
209 
210  if (object_recognition_client_)
211  {
212  try
213  {
214  waitForAction(object_recognition_client_, nh_, ros::Duration(3.0), OBJECT_RECOGNITION_ACTION);
215  }
216  catch (std::exception& ex)
217  {
218  // ROS_ERROR("Object recognition action: %s", ex.what());
219  object_recognition_client_.reset();
220  }
221  }
222 
223  try
224  {
225  const planning_scene_monitor::LockedPlanningSceneRO& ps = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO();
226  if (ps)
227  {
228  semantic_world_ = std::make_shared<moveit::semantic_world::SemanticWorld>(ps);
229  }
230  else
231  semantic_world_.reset();

233  {
234  semantic_world_->addTableCallback(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::updateTables, this));
235  }
236  }
237  catch (std::exception& ex)
238  {
239  ROS_ERROR("%s", ex.what());
240  }

260 void MotionPlanningFrame::allowExternalProgramCommunication(bool enable)
261 {
262  // This is needed to prevent UI event (resuming the options) triggered
263  // before getRobotInteraction() is loaded and ready
264  if (first_time_)
265  return;
266 
267  planning_display_->getRobotInteraction()->toggleMoveInteractiveMarkerTopic(enable);
268  planning_display_->toggleSelectPlanningGroupSubscription(enable);
269  if (enable)
270  {
271  ros::NodeHandle nh;
272  plan_subscriber_ = nh.subscribe("/rviz/moveit/plan", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remotePlanCallback, this);
273  execute_subscriber_ = nh.subscribe("/rviz/moveit/execute", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteExecuteCallback, this);
274  stop_subscriber_ = nh.subscribe("/rviz/moveit/stop", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteStopCallback, this);
275  update_start_state_subscriber_ =
276  nh.subscribe("/rviz/moveit/update_start_state", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteUpdateStartStateCallback, this);
277  update_goal_state_subscriber_ =
278  nh.subscribe("/rviz/moveit/update_goal_state", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteUpdateGoalStateCallback, this);
279  update_custom_start_state_subscriber_ = nh.subscribe(
280  "/rviz/moveit/update_custom_start_state", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteUpdateCustomStartStateCallback, this);
281  update_custom_goal_state_subscriber_ = nh.subscribe(
282  "/rviz/moveit/update_custom_goal_state", 1, &MotionPlanningFrame::remoteUpdateCustomGoalStateCallback, this);
283  }
284  else
285  { // disable
286  plan_subscriber_.shutdown();
287  execute_subscriber_.shutdown();
288  stop_subscriber_.shutdown();
289  update_start_state_subscriber_.shutdown();
290  update_goal_state_subscriber_.shutdown();
291  update_custom_start_state_subscriber_.shutdown();
292  update_custom_goal_state_subscriber_.shutdown();
293  }
294 }

296 void MotionPlanningFrame::fillPlanningGroupOptions()
297 {
298  const QSignalBlocker planning_group_blocker(ui_->planning_group_combo_box);
299  ui_->planning_group_combo_box->clear();
300 
301  const moveit::core::RobotModelConstPtr& kmodel = planning_display_->getRobotModel();
302  for (const std::string& group_name : kmodel->getJointModelGroupNames())
303  ui_->planning_group_combo_box->addItem(QString::fromStdString(group_name));
304 }
305 
306 void MotionPlanningFrame::fillStateSelectionOptions()
307 {
308  const QSignalBlocker start_state_blocker(ui_->start_state_combo_box);
309  const QSignalBlocker goal_state_blocker(ui_->goal_state_combo_box);
310  ui_->start_state_combo_box->clear();
311  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->clear();
312 
313  if (!planning_display_->getPlanningSceneMonitor())
314  return;
315 
316  const moveit::core::RobotModelConstPtr& robot_model = planning_display_->getRobotModel();
317  std::string group = planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup();
318  if (group.empty())
319  return;
320  const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg = robot_model->getJointModelGroup(group);
321  if (jmg)
322  {
323  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<random valid>"));
324  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<random>"));
325  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<current>"));
326  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<same as goal>"));
327  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<previous>"));
328 
329  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<random valid>"));
330  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<random>"));
331  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<current>"));
332  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<same as start>"));
333  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString("<previous>"));
334 
335  const std::vector<std::string>& known_states = jmg->getDefaultStateNames();
336  if (!known_states.empty())
337  {
338  ui_->start_state_combo_box->insertSeparator(ui_->start_state_combo_box->count());
339  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->insertSeparator(ui_->goal_state_combo_box->count());
340  for (const std::string& known_state : known_states)
341  {
342  ui_->start_state_combo_box->addItem(QString::fromStdString(known_state));
343  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->addItem(QString::fromStdString(known_state));
344  }
345  }
346 
347  ui_->start_state_combo_box->setCurrentIndex(2); // default to 'current'
348  ui_->goal_state_combo_box->setCurrentIndex(2); // default to 'current'
349  }
350 }

352 void MotionPlanningFrame::changePlanningGroupHelper()
353 {
354  if (!planning_display_->getPlanningSceneMonitor())
355  return;
356 
357  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::fillStateSelectionOptions, this));
358  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
359  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populateConstraintsList, this, std::vector<std::string>()));
360 
361  const moveit::core::RobotModelConstPtr& robot_model = planning_display_->getRobotModel();
362  std::string group = planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup();
363  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
364  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningParamWidget::setGroupName, ui_->planner_param_treeview, group));
365  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
366  [=]() { ui_->planning_group_combo_box->setCurrentText(QString::fromStdString(group)); });
367 
368  if (!group.empty() && robot_model)
369  {
370  if (move_group_ && move_group_->getName() == group)
371  return;
372  ROS_INFO("Constructing new MoveGroup connection for group '%s' in namespace '%s'", group.c_str(),
373  planning_display_->getMoveGroupNS().c_str());
374  moveit::planning_interface::MoveGroupInterface::Options opt(group);
375  opt.robot_model_ = robot_model;
376  opt.robot_description_.clear();
377  opt.node_handle_ = ros::NodeHandle(planning_display_->getMoveGroupNS());
378  try
379  {
380 #ifdef RVIZ_TF1
381  std::shared_ptr<tf2_ros::Buffer> tf_buffer = moveit::planning_interface::getSharedTF();
382 #else
383  std::shared_ptr<tf2_ros::Buffer> tf_buffer = context_->getFrameManager()->getTF2BufferPtr();
384 #endif
385  move_group_ =
386  std::make_shared<moveit::planning_interface::MoveGroupInterface>(opt, tf_buffer, ros::WallDuration(30, 0));
387 
388  if (planning_scene_storage_)
389  move_group_->setConstraintsDatabase(ui_->database_host->text().toStdString(), ui_->database_port->value());
390  }
391  catch (std::exception& ex)
392  {
393  ROS_ERROR("%s", ex.what());
394  }
395  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
396  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningParamWidget::setMoveGroup, ui_->planner_param_treeview, move_group_));
397  if (move_group_)
398  {
399  move_group_->allowLooking(ui_->allow_looking->isChecked());
400  move_group_->allowReplanning(ui_->allow_replanning->isChecked());
401  bool has_unique_endeffector = !move_group_->getEndEffectorLink().empty();
402  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob([=]() { ui_->use_cartesian_path->setEnabled(has_unique_endeffector); });
403  std::vector<moveit_msgs::PlannerInterfaceDescription> desc;
404  if (move_group_->getInterfaceDescriptions(desc))
405  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlannersList, this, desc));
406  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populateConstraintsList, this),
407  "populateConstraintsList");
408 
409  if (first_time_)
410  {
411  first_time_ = false;
412  const planning_scene_monitor::LockedPlanningSceneRO& ps = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO();
413  if (ps)
414  {
415  planning_display_->setQueryStartState(ps->getCurrentState());
416  planning_display_->setQueryGoalState(ps->getCurrentState());
417  }
418  // This ensures saved UI settings applied after planning_display_ is ready
419  planning_display_->useApproximateIK(ui_->approximate_ik->isChecked());
420  if (ui_->allow_external_program->isChecked())
421  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
422  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::allowExternalProgramCommunication, this, true));
423  }
424  }
425  }
426 }

428 void MotionPlanningFrame::changePlanningGroup()
429 {
430  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::changePlanningGroupHelper, this),

433  planning_display_->getQueryStartStateHandler(),
434  planning_display_->getQueryGoalStateHandler());

443 void MotionPlanningFrame::addSceneObject()
444 {
445  static const double MIN_VAL = 1e-6;
446 
447  if (!planning_display_->getPlanningSceneMonitor())
448  {
449  return;
450  }
451 
452  // get size values
453  double x_length = ui_->shape_size_x_spin_box->isEnabled() ? ui_->shape_size_x_spin_box->value() : MIN_VAL;
454  double y_length = ui_->shape_size_y_spin_box->isEnabled() ? ui_->shape_size_y_spin_box->value() : MIN_VAL;
455  double z_length = ui_->shape_size_z_spin_box->isEnabled() ? ui_->shape_size_z_spin_box->value() : MIN_VAL;
456  if (x_length < MIN_VAL || y_length < MIN_VAL || z_length < MIN_VAL)
457  {
458  QMessageBox::warning(this, QString("Dimension is too small"), QString("Size values need to be >= %1").arg(MIN_VAL));
459  return;
460  }
461 
462  // by default, name object by shape type
463  std::string selected_shape = ui_->shapes_combo_box->currentText().toStdString();
464  shapes::ShapeConstPtr shape;
465  switch (ui_->shapes_combo_box->currentData().toInt()) // fetch shape ID from current combobox item
466  {
467  case shapes::BOX:
468  shape = std::make_shared<shapes::Box>(x_length, y_length, z_length);
469  break;
470  case shapes::SPHERE:
471  shape = std::make_shared<shapes::Sphere>(0.5 * x_length);
472  break;
473  case shapes::CONE:
474  shape = std::make_shared<shapes::Cone>(0.5 * x_length, z_length);
475  break;
476  case shapes::CYLINDER:
477  shape = std::make_shared<shapes::Cylinder>(0.5 * x_length, z_length);
478  break;
479  case shapes::MESH:
480  {
481  QUrl url;
482  if (ui_->shapes_combo_box->currentText().contains("file")) // open from file
483  url = QFileDialog::getOpenFileUrl(this, tr("Import Object Mesh"), QString(),
484  "CAD files (*.stl *.obj *.dae);;All files (*.*)");
485  else // open from URL
486  url = QInputDialog::getText(this, tr("Import Object Mesh"), tr("URL for file to import from:"),
487  QLineEdit::Normal, QString("http://"));
488  if (!url.isEmpty())
489  shape = loadMeshResource(url.toString().toStdString());
490  if (!shape)
491  return;
492  // name mesh objects by their file name
493  selected_shape = url.fileName().toStdString();
494  break;
495  }
496  default:
497  QMessageBox::warning(this, QString("Unsupported shape"),
498  QString("The '%1' is not supported.").arg(ui_->shapes_combo_box->currentText()));
499  }
500 
501  // find available (initial) name of object
502  int idx = 0;
503  std::string shape_name = selected_shape + "_" + std::to_string(idx);
504  while (planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO()->getWorld()->hasObject(shape_name))
505  {
506  idx++;
507  shape_name = selected_shape + "_" + std::to_string(idx);
508  }
509 
510  // Actually add object to the plugin's PlanningScene
511  {
512  planning_scene_monitor::LockedPlanningSceneRW ps = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRW();
513  ps->getWorldNonConst()->addToObject(shape_name, shape, Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
514  }
515  setLocalSceneEdited();
516 
517  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populateCollisionObjectsList, this));
518 
519  // Automatically select the inserted object so that its IM is displayed
520  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(
521  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::setItemSelectionInList, this, shape_name, true, ui_->collision_objects_list));
522 
523  planning_display_->queueRenderSceneGeometry();
524 }
525 
526 shapes::ShapePtr MotionPlanningFrame::loadMeshResource(const std::string& url)
527 {
528  shapes::Mesh* mesh = shapes::createMeshFromResource(url);
529  if (mesh)
530  {
531  // If the object is very large, ask the user if the scale should be reduced.
532  bool object_is_very_large = false;
533  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < mesh->vertex_count; i++)
534  {
535  if ((abs(mesh->vertices[i * 3 + 0]) > LARGE_MESH_THRESHOLD) ||
536  (abs(mesh->vertices[i * 3 + 1]) > LARGE_MESH_THRESHOLD) ||
537  (abs(mesh->vertices[i * 3 + 2]) > LARGE_MESH_THRESHOLD))
538  {
539  object_is_very_large = true;
540  break;
541  }
542  }
543  if (object_is_very_large)
544  {
545  QMessageBox msg_box;
546  msg_box.setText(
547  "The object is very large (greater than 10 m). The file may be in millimeters instead of meters.");
548  msg_box.setInformativeText("Attempt to fix the size by shrinking the object?");
549  msg_box.setStandardButtons(QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
550  msg_box.setDefaultButton(QMessageBox::Yes);
551  if (msg_box.exec() == QMessageBox::Yes)
552  {
553  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < mesh->vertex_count; ++i)
554  {
555  unsigned int i3 = i * 3;
556  mesh->vertices[i3] *= 0.001;
557  mesh->vertices[i3 + 1] *= 0.001;
558  mesh->vertices[i3 + 2] *= 0.001;
559  }
560  }
561  }
562 
563  return shapes::ShapePtr(mesh);
564  }
565  else
566  {
567  QMessageBox::warning(this, QString("Import error"), QString("Unable to import object"));
568  return shapes::ShapePtr();
569  }
570 }
